  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "The iPool (Gao et al. 2021b) selects key nodes in the graph through information-based scoring and selection strategies to build graph representations with rich expressive ability and hierarchical structure.",
    "VIPool (Li et al. 2020) achieves node selection by using the maximization of mutual information on the graph to select neighboring nodes that it can represent locally.",
    "Pool (Pang et al. 2021) maximizes the mutual information between the input graph and the coarsened graph to achieve the coarsening graph selection.",
    "Pool (Li et al. 2023a) adaptively implements node selection by introducing multi-view information and deep reinforcement learning.",
    "SSPool (Li et al. 2023b) implements coarsening graph selection by maximizing mutual information between the coarsening graph and the perturbed coarsening graph."
  ],
